{"tid":1537832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議員辦事處被人玻壞 民建聯區議員：是「示威者」惡意破壞","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:04.000Z","uid":212626,"like":13,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6b5a045df35334b0386b11f4f1f1f2c0dfd283","tid":1537832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"民建聯區議員曾憲康位於屯門友愛邨的議員辦事處昨晚被人玻壞，曾憲康在facebook上稱是<span style=\"color: red;\">「示威者」所為</span>，從圖片可見，曾憲康議辦的門窗、枱櫈、電腦及閉路電視等遭到損毀，物件散落一地。<br />\n<br />\n曾憲康表示已就事件報警，批評有關違法行為已超出市民所能接受的尺度，攻擊破壞不同意見者的辦事處，只會將社會推向不復之地，支持警方繼續嚴正執法，而他自己會繼續服務市民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e8%ad%b0%e8%be%a6%e9%81%ad%e7%a0%b4%e5%a3%9e-187490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e8%25be%25a6%25e9%2581%25ad%25e7%25a0%25b4%25e5%25a3%259e-187490&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=8356033b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e8%ad%b0%e8%be%a6%e9%81%ad%e7%a0%b4%e5%a3%9e-187490</a>"},{"pid":"79bbc009a8b5b38fc9234aac226dbc73ae8b83a4","tid":1537832,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<b